      "name": "rate-limiting",
      "description": "pme:ip: limiter \u2014 burst=10, rate=10/1min (0.1667 t/s).\nAll 10 warmup requests use the valid access_token from setup (JWT auth fires before the limiter\ninside the JWT middleware group). 11th request \u2192 429 too_many_requests, Retry-After=6.\n\nRequires Redis flushed (make _e2e-kv-clean) before this folder.",
